rows.label: qst202403_msg0001
rows.name:
The Nopon Trade Guild ID should
be somewhere around here...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202403_msg0002
rows.name:
Everyone, look, look! There's a
weird-shaped rock over here!

rows.label: qst202403_msg0022
rows.name:
[ML:Dash ]Ibuki, that's not what we're
looking for right now, is it?

rows.label: qst202403_msg0023
rows.name: Huh? Wasn't it?

rows.label: qst202403_msg0024
rows.name:
We're supposed to find the
Nopon Trade Guild ID that
Noganga-san told us about.

rows.label: qst202403_msg0025
rows.name:
Now that you mention
it, that might be it.

rows.label: qst202403_msg0003
rows.name: You there! What are you doing here?!

rows.label: qst202403_msg0004
rows.name:
We've been spotted!
Everyone, get ready!

rows.label: qst202403_msg0005
rows.name: [ML:Dash ]They're not attacking.

rows.label: qst202403_msg0006
rows.name:
What's going on...?[ML:Dash ] Is
it some kind of trap?

rows.label: qst202403_msg0007
rows.name: Kountess! We found the Kountess!

rows.label: qst202403_msg0008
rows.name: The Kountess has returned!

rows.label: qst202403_msg0009
rows.name: We must inform the King!

rows.label: qst202403_msg0010
rows.name:
But the King has already
headed to Avaritia!

rows.label: qst202403_msg0011
rows.name: Right, that's true!

rows.label: qst202403_msg0012
rows.name:
But the Kountess has
returned! This is great!

rows.label: qst202403_msg0013
rows.name: Great! Kountess!

rows.label: qst202403_msg0014
rows.name: Hey, what is it?! I'm not a Tirkin!

rows.label: qst202403_msg0015
rows.name:
That can't be true! You're
definitely the Kountess!

rows.label: qst202403_msg0016
rows.name: Kountess!

rows.label: qst202403_msg0017
rows.name: Oh, come on! Be quiet, be quiet!

rows.label: qst202403_msg0018
rows.name: What's happening?

rows.label: qst202403_msg0019
rows.name:
Are they mistaking Ibuki
for someone else?

rows.label: qst202403_msg0020
rows.name:
It would seem so...[ML:Dash ] But at this
rate, we won't be able to find
the Nopon Trade Guild ID.

rows.label: qst202403_msg0021
rows.name:
I feel bad for the Tirkin, but we'll
have to make them quiet down...[ML:Dash ]
